Package backEnd

Class Island

java.lang.Object
backEnd.Island
public class Island
extends java.lang.Object
Island is either home or destination for a ship. There are 5 in total.
Each has a shop and 2 routes to each of the other islands.
Author:
Aerinn Nguyen, Bede Skinner-Vennell
